<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ880927-0080 </DOCNO><HL> Notable andamp; Quotable </HL><SO> </SO><TEXT>      Ralph E. Gomory, senior vice president for science and technology at IBM, quoted in the summer 1988 Issues in Science and Technology:   Although I don't know how many people need to understand science, my guess is that it's a minority. What we really need, in my opinion, is to educate everyone in the three R's, which we clearly don't do well enough today. </TEXT></DOC>